Texts.Eng: Next time fishman whine at you about their numberssss, just lay that on em. Maybe only 10% ssssurvive, but ssstill enough to fight Floran war instead of becoming lunch.

Sssso, Floransss gotta ssssecret. Hylotl never wasss in danger. Think about it. What fish do naturally? Lay a lot of eggsssss. Hylotl are fishpeople. Floran not sssure how there ssso many Floran or how more are made, But sssmelly butt fishman? Eggsss out the wazoo.
